{"id":"claim-01","prompt":"You wrote that the system improved accuracy by 22%. Defend the claim.","required_evidence":["metric definition","dataset and denominator","baseline and final configuration","slice results","development or holdout status","limitations"]}
{"id":"ownership-01","prompt":"Show code generated by a coding agent that you corrected.","required_evidence":["original risk or error","contract used to judge it","patch or rejection","focused and regression tests","oral explanation"]}
{"id":"architecture-01","prompt":"Why is this an agent and why is LangGraph justified?","required_evidence":["multi-step state or tool need","interrupt/recovery need","simpler alternative considered","cost of framework","behavioral test"]}
{"id":"production-01","prompt":"What prevents this from being production-ready?","required_evidence":["intended context","release blockers","security and privacy gaps","operations gaps","accepted prototype risks","highest-value next work"]}
{"id":"failure-01","prompt":"Demonstrate one success path and two failure or recovery paths.","required_evidence":["fixture-backed reproducibility","correlation trace","expected state transitions","no unauthorized side effect","documented result"]}
